name: MetalMoney
0:
”Alexa, ask metal money how much gold costs”
”Alexa, ask metal money, what is the price of iridium?”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: metal money
des: Ask about the price of a metal and get a price reported in the past few days. You can ask about the price of gold, silver, copper, platinum, iridium, iron, and zinc.
